                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Heureux qui peut se dire illustre !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Du temps que j'en étais épris,\nLes lauriers valaient bien leur prix.\nÀ coup sûr on n'est pas un rustre\nLe jour où l'on voit imprimés\nLes poëmes qu'on a rimés :\nHeureux qui peut se dire illustre !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Moi-même un instant je le fus.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "J'ai comme un souvenir confus",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "D'avoir embrassé la Chimère.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "J'ai mangé du sucre candi",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Dans les feuilletons du lundi :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Ma bouche en est encor amère.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Moi-même un instant je le fus.\nJ'ai comme un souvenir confus\nD'avoir embrassé la Chimère.\nJ'ai mangé du sucre candi\nDans les feuilletons du lundi :\nMa bouche en est encor amère."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Quittons nos lyres, Érato !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "On n'entend plus que le râteau",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "De la roulette et de la banque ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Viens devant ce peuple qui bout",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Jouer du violon debout",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Sur l'échelle du saltimbanque !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Quittons nos lyres, Érato !\nOn n'entend plus que le râteau\nDe la roulette et de la banque ;\nViens devant ce peuple qui bout\nJouer du violon debout\nSur l'échelle du saltimbanque !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Car, si jamais ses yeux vermeils",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Ne sont las de voir les soleils",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Sans baisser leurs fauves paupières,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Le poëte n'est pas toujours",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "En train de réjouir les ours",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Et de civiliser les pierres.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Car, si jamais ses yeux vermeils\nNe sont las de voir les soleils\nSans baisser leurs fauves paupières,\nLe poëte n'est pas toujours\nEn train de réjouir les ours\nEt de civiliser les pierres."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "En vain les accords de sa voix",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Ont charmé les monstres ; parfois",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Loin des flots sacrés il émigre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Las, sinon guéri de prêcher",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "L'amour aux côtes du rocher",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Et la douceur aux dents du tigre.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "En vain les accords de sa voix\nOnt charmé les monstres ; parfois\nLoin des flots sacrés il émigre,\nLas, sinon guéri de prêcher\nL'amour aux côtes du rocher\nEt la douceur aux dents du tigre."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Il se demande s'il n'est plus,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Sous les vieux arbres chevelus",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "De cette France que nous sommes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "De l'Océan au pont de Kehl,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Un déguisement sous lequel",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "On puisse parler à des hommes ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il se demande s'il n'est plus,\nSous les vieux arbres chevelus\nDe cette France que nous sommes,\nDe l'Océan au pont de Kehl,\nUn déguisement sous lequel\nOn puisse parler à des hommes ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Et, voulant protester du moins",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Devant les immortels témoins",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "En faveur des dieux qu'on renie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Quoique son âme soit ailleurs,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Il te prend tes masques railleurs",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Et ton rire, ô sainte ironie !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et, voulant protester du moins\nDevant les immortels témoins\nEn faveur des dieux qu'on renie,\nQuoique son âme soit ailleurs,\nIl te prend tes masques railleurs\nEt ton rire, ô sainte ironie !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Alors, sur son triste haillon",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Il coud des morceaux de paillon,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Pour que dans ce siècle profane,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Fût-ce en manière de jouet,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "On lui permette encor le fouet",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "De son aïeul Aristophane.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Alors, sur son triste haillon\nIl coud des morceaux de paillon,\nPour que dans ce siècle profane,\nFût-ce en manière de jouet,\nOn lui permette encor le fouet\nDe son aïeul Aristophane."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Et d'une lieue on l'aperçoit",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "En souliers rouges ! Mais qu'il soit",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Un héros sublime ou grotesque ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Ô muse ! Qu'il chasse aux vautours,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Ou qu'il daigne faire des tours",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Sur la corde funambulesque,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et d'une lieue on l'aperçoit\nEn souliers rouges ! Mais qu'il soit\nUn héros sublime ou grotesque ;\nÔ muse ! Qu'il chasse aux vautours,\nOu qu'il daigne faire des tours\nSur la corde funambulesque,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Tribun, prophète ou baladin,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Toujours fuyant avec dédain",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Ces pavés que le passant foule,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Il marche sur les fiers sommets",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Ou sur la corde ignoble, mais",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Au-dessus des fronts de la foule.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tribun, prophète ou baladin,\nToujours fuyant avec dédain\nCes pavés que le passant foule,\nIl marche sur les fiers sommets\nOu sur la corde ignoble, mais\nAu-dessus des fronts de la foule."
        }
    ],
